WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:57.100
The [SSID] and [Password] will appear on the camera.

00:00:58.300 --> 00:01:08.700
Open the Wi-Fi setup screen of your iPhone/iPad.

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:17.900
Set your iPhone/iPad for Wi-Fi connection.

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:25.000
Select the detected camera (DIRECT-xxxx:xxx-xxx).

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:36.300
Enter the password displayed on the camera 
in your iPhone/iPad.

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:50.100
Your camera and iPhone/iPad will establish 
a connection.

00:01:50.600 --> 00:02:01.800
Start PlayMemories Mobile™ on your iPhone/iPad.

00:02:02.300 --> 00:02:06.900
Register the camera for automatic transfer of 
still images on PlayMemories Mobile™.

00:02:14.700 --> 00:02:17.800
The camera has been registered.

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:46.100
Follow these procedures to return to 
the shooting screen.

00:02:50.700 --> 00:02:58.900
Shoot a still image with your camera.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:05.600
Bring the iPhone/iPad you registered as the transfer 
destination near the camera.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:10.900
Switch off your camera.

00:03:14.100 --> 00:03:25.200
From the Wi-Fi setup screen, select the SSID of 
the camera and check the Wi-Fi connection.

00:03:25.900 --> 00:03:38.800
Return to the home screen and start PlayMemories Mobile™. 
The camera will transfer the still image.

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:43.500
When the transfer is completed, the camera will 
automatically shut off. 

00:03:56.900 --> 00:04:10.200
You can view the transferred still images 
with applications.

